Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.88,0:15:42.67,AKT,,0000,0000,0000,,Halo?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.67,0:15:44.67,AKT,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yoshiyuki? Prečo....
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.67,0:15:46.30,AKT,,0000,0000,0000,,No, vieš...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.30,0:15:48.05,AKT,,0000,0000,0000,,Je tam Nanaka?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.05,0:15:49.05,AKT,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo tým myslíš?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.05,0:15:52.76,AKT,,0000,0000,0000,,Rodičia Nanaky mi volali. Ešte neprišla domov.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.34,0:15:54.52,AKT,,0000,0000,0000,,Naozaj?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.52,0:15:56.35,AKT,,0000,0000,0000,,Hej, kde si teraz?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.35,0:15:58.06,AKT,,0000,0000,0000,,Kde? Som v škole...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.02,0:16:01.36,AKT,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo? Halo? Koko?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.19,0:16:06.69,AKT,,0000,0000,0000,,Prečo práve teraz?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.95,0:16:10.41,AKT,,0000,0000,0000,,Halo? Koko?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.79,0:16:15.43,AKT,,0000,0000,0000,,Nanaka...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.43,0:16:17.58,AKT,,0000,0000,0000,,Mohla by byť ešte vo škole?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.58,0:16:19.54,AKT,,0000,0000,0000,,Halo? Halo?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.54,0:16:21.68,Distant Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Číslo, ktoré voláte je momentálne nedostupné,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.68,0:16:24.95,Distant Text,,0000,0000,0000,,buď preto, že je vypnutý alebo nie je v dosahu signál.
