Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.72,0:16:33.38,AKT,,0000,0000,0000,,Yoshiyuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.35,0:16:36.60,AKT,,0000,0000,0000,,Hej! Nanaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.38,0:16:36.60,sign,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs29\frx12\fry26\frz348.192\c&H040000&\pos(348,301)}Hudobná trieda
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.27,0:16:38.56,AKT,,0000,0000,0000,,Si tu?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.31,0:16:41.06,AKT,,0000,0000,0000,,Nanaka! Ak si tu, odpovedz!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.65,0:16:45.48,AKT,,0000,0000,0000,,Kde by mohla byť?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.74,0:16:50.40,AKT,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, toto? Premýšľala som, že dnes budem cvičiť sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.41,0:16:52.61,AKT,,0000,0000,0000,,Cvičiť spev.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.38,0:17:04.79,AKT,,0000,0000,0000,,To je problém...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.22,0:17:12.68,AKT,,0000,0000,0000,,Yoshiyuki-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.22,0:17:17.68,AKT,,0000,0000,0000,,Nanaka! Si tam?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.64,0:17:22.27,AKT,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yoshiyuki-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.27,0:17:23.23,AKT,,0000,0000,0000,,Yoshiyuki-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.81,0:17:25.71,AKT,,0000,0000,0000,,Nanaka! Čo tam robíš?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.71,0:17:27.69,AKT,,0000,0000,0000,,Dvere nejdú otvoriť.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.69,0:17:28.90,AKT,,0000,0000,0000,,Naozaj?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.07,0:17:35.41,AKT,,0000,0000,0000,,Sú zaseknuté? Čo sa to sakra stalo?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.99,0:17:37.87,AKT,,0000,0000,0000,,Náhle sa zdvihol vietor a dvere sa zabuchli...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.87,0:17:40.20,AKT,,0000,0000,0000,,Rozumiem! Odstúp!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.76,0:17:50.92,AKT,,0000,0000,0000,,Yoshiyuki-kun, neprežeň to!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.92,0:17:52.50,AKT,,0000,0000,0000,,Vydrž, už to bude!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.30,0:17:57.55,AKT,,0000,0000,0000,,Yoshiyuki-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.06,0:18:01.68,AKT,,0000,0000,0000,,Som rád, že si v poriadku.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.52,0:18:09.86,AKT,,0000,0000,0000,,Ďakujem ti, že si prišiel.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.86,0:18:12.57,AKT,,0000,0000,0000,,Tak, poďme dnu.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.37,0:18:19.99,AKT,,0000,0000,0000,,Prečo si išla na strechu?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.99,0:18:24.12,AKT,,0000,0000,0000,,Nemohla som použiť hudobnú triedu, tak...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.12,0:18:26.83,AKT,,0000,0000,0000,,Tak si potom mala ísť domov.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.84,0:18:29.50,AKT,,0000,0000,0000,,Ďakujem ti.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.50,0:18:32.13,AKT,,0000,0000,0000,,Vieš, že sa blíži tajfún.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.13,0:18:38.50,AKT,,0000,0000,0000,,Ja len, že včerajšie cvičenie nedopadlo veľmi dobre.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.50,0:18:40.06,AKT,,0000,0000,0000,,Je to divné.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.06,0:18:45.77,AKT,,0000,0000,0000,,V myšlienkach som bola niekde inde a tak som sa nemohla sústrediť.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.81,0:18:51.15,AKT,,0000,0000,0000,,Hovoril som ti, aby si si nerobila starosti ohľadom tých rečí.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.15,0:18:53.11,AKT,,0000,0000,0000,,Nie, tak to nieje.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.11,0:18:59.37,AKT,,0000,0000,0000,,Preto som chcela spievať, aby moje hlasivky odfúkli ten smútok.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.37,0:19:00.78,AKT,,0000,0000,0000,,Prepáč.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.62,0:19:07.39,AKT,,0000,0000,0000,,No, odfúknuť starosti je v poriadku, pokiaľ sa o tebe neboja ostatný.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.39,0:19:09.54,AKT,,0000,0000,0000,,Naozaj si ma vystrašila.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.54,0:19:10.98,AKT,,0000,0000,0000,,Prepáč.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.98,0:19:11.83,AKT,,0000,0000,0000,,Ale...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.84,0:19:14.55,AKT,,0000,0000,0000,,Som tak šťastná.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.26,0:19:18.47,AKT,,0000,0000,0000,,Bála som sa, že by ma nikto neprišiel zachrániť,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.47,0:19:22.64,AKT,,0000,0000,0000,,ale myslela som, že by si mohol prísť ty.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.64,0:19:24.22,AKT,,0000,0000,0000,,Predstavovala som si to.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.23,0:19:27.60,AKT,,0000,0000,0000,,A potom si sa objavil!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.60,0:19:29.09,AKT,,0000,0000,0000,,Bola som tak prekvapená.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.63,0:19:30.65,AKT,,0000,0000,0000,,Je to len náhoda.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.65,0:19:33.61,AKT,,0000,0000,0000,,Naozaj som veľmi šťastná!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.16,0:19:40.62,AKT,,0000,0000,0000,,Hej, si v poriadku?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.62,0:19:42.78,AKT,,0000,0000,0000,,Áno, som.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.79,0:19:46.83,AKT,,0000,0000,0000,,Poďme domov. Inak tu prechladneš.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.83,0:19:49.79,AKT,,0000,0000,0000,,Si tak milý, Yoshiyuki-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.50,0:19:54.84,AKT,,0000,0000,0000,,Chápem, prečo sa Koko do teba zamilovala, Yoshiyuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.34,0:19:58.01,AKT,,0000,0000,0000,,Nanaka?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.53,0:20:03.26,AKT,,0000,0000,0000,,Naozaj tomu rozumiem.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.60,0:20:11.02,AKT,,0000,0000,0000,,Ak sa neosušíš, tak naozaj prechladneš.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.07,0:20:16.94,AKT,,0000,0000,0000,,Yoshiyuki-kun, ja...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.94,0:20:18.24,AKT,,0000,0000,0000,,Ja...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.03,0:20:22.16,AKT,,0000,0000,0000,,Nanaka?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.00,0:20:30.46,Distant Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Chápem.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.46,0:20:36.09,Distant Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Mal o mňa strach len preto, lebo...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.47,0:20:44.01,Distant Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Lebo sme len kamaráti.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.89,0:20:49.24,AKT,,0000,0000,0000,,Nanaka?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.48,0:20:52.64,AKT,,0000,0000,0000,,To nič nie je.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.23,0:20:57.30,AKT,,0000,0000,0000,,Yoshiyuki-kun, ty si milý na každého.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.95,0:21:03.32,AKT,,0000,0000,0000,,Je to dobrá vlastnosť, ale môžeš tým aj zraňovať iných ľudí!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.37,0:21:07.00,AKT,,0000,0000,0000,,Pamätaj si to!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.00,0:21:08.50,AKT,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, áno.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.47,0:21:12.67,AKT,,0000,0000,0000,,Postaraj sa o Koko, dobre?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.67,0:21:14.42,AKT,,0000,0000,0000,,Rozumiem.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.01,0:21:26.05,AKT,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, to je Koko!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.06,0:21:28.02,AKT,,0000,0000,0000,,Tiež sa o teba bála...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.56,0:21:31.52,AKT,,0000,0000,0000,,Tu, Yoshiyuki-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.52,0:21:32.44,AKT,,0000,0000,0000,,Koko!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.07,0:21:44.28,AKT,,0000,0000,0000,,Nanaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.16,0:21:47.08,AKT,,0000,0000,0000,,Áno!
